            Microsoft
            Graph and replace.
            <ul>
                <li>Value of <b>{DisplayName}</b> with your app displayed name. For example, <i>Woodgrove Groceries</i>
                </li>
                <li>Values of the <b>{RedirectUris}</b> with the redirect URI of your application. For example,
